description: The index is a rules-based index that consists of a tiered, modified market capitalization-weighted portfolio of U.S.-listed equity securities, of companies whose products and services are economically tied to the market’s adoption of 5G networking and communication technologies. The fund invests at least 80% of its net assets in financial instruments and ETFs that track the index and other financial instruments that provide daily leveraged exposure to the index or to ETFs that track the index. It is non-diversified.
name: Direxion Daily 5G Communications Bull 2X Shares
